  <div><h3 class="font-bold">Does MLGW offer solar rebates?</h3><p>MLGW doesn't offer direct solar rebates but provides net metering allowing you to sell excess power back to the grid. They do offer rebates up to \$500 for high-efficiency HVAC equipment and free energy audits. Combined with the federal 30% tax credit and Tennessee's property tax exemption for solar, Memphis residents have substantial incentive opportunities.</p></div>
  
